{"tid":761514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"對曼聯的倒掛？沙基利：常規動作吧","createTime":"2018-07-30T12:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T13:18:57.000Z","uid":161311,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"053b532e7c7d0f97f993ea41d4d7d622e81c645d","tid":761514,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"熱身賽對曼聯攻入倒勾後，沙基利告訴利物浦官網稱這只是常規操作。<br />\n<br />\n　　在利物浦4-1擊敗曼聯的熱身賽中，紅軍新援沙基利攻入一個倒勾，成為比賽最大的看點。<br />\n<br />\n    　賽後他表示：「我認為我已經習慣了倒勾。我攻入了很多這樣的入球，我喜歡倒勾，所以經常在比賽中練習倒勾。隊友的傳球很棒，為什麼不試試呢？所以我就試了一把，這是一個漂亮的入球。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「這是很棒的一天，球場里有很多球迷，這是我代表利物浦的首場比賽，我很開心，當然還有這個漂亮的倒勾。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「這是一家大球會，我要展示我的足球，你們在場上可以看到，我也很有經驗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180730/4/19/2/對曼聯的倒掛-利物浦新援-常規動作吧-9080077.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F4%2F19%2F2%2F%E5%B0%8D%E6%9B%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%80%92%E6%8E%9B-%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6%E6%96%B0%E6%8F%B4-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8F%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E5%90%A7-9080077.html&d=ECuEBLj9%2FHVn5cERnK52mv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c69ce6fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180730/4/19/2/對曼聯的倒掛-利物浦新援-常規動作吧-9080077.html</a>"},{"pid":"defb0f8fc57d64dc99d79888e3aa3c490e239c7e","tid":761514,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"唔識volley淨係識倒掛"},{"pid":"c50e18cb939261df75c75a2d029131f40c143342","tid":761514,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"defb0f8fc57d64dc99d79888e3aa3c490e239c7e","tid":761514,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:32:29.000Z","msg":"唔識volley淨係識倒掛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f1453283e380e75491188e967a4c83e5f05f4d","tid":761514,"uid":97223,"like